                            <comment id="96132" author="olivergierke" created="Thu, 5 Dec 2013 01:48:56 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I fixed this by gracefully falling back to the defaults (in case of invalid page number and size) or ignoring invalid values (for sort properties). I think this makes more sense rather than telling the client that it was wrong and it has to repeat the request, which it would then do using the defaults anyway.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="96137" author="kazukishimizu" created="Thu, 5 Dec 2013 04:51:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Great!!&lt;br/&gt;
I agree a that apply the default value.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
